{"tid":698505,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知有無人同我一樣，有種身分認同嘅迷惘？","createTime":"2018-06-11T17:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T02:11:52.000Z","uid":148363,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b984ba9874664ae52c41874c74581ab443e5093a","tid":698505,"uid":148363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T17:57:27.000Z","msg":"近來發現自己既唔係中國人亦唔係英國人，甚至乎唔係香港人。當你聲稱你係某個地方嘅人，並唔係因為你嘅血統或者出世地去決定，而係你有無同呢個地方有共同嘅意志，睇法同信念。近年我真係攪唔清咩先係香港人，如果我同人講我係香港人，佢地會唔會意為我好似電視見到個班一樣，甘醜陋。但我又唔認為佢地係香港人嘅大多數，我原來只係出生係呢度嘅異數，甘我又係咩人呢？"},{"pid":"8b9ae5dfa46b88c36c3a3b27fc1d5429dae31b75","tid":698505,"uid":174601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T18:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> who cares"},{"pid":"babaf66c50b11334b9f1cd4914d42555bfcad1c2","tid":698505,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T18:12:05.000Z","msg":"你咪一條毒撚，完<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇得自己那麼高.jpg 召喚"},{"pid":"4bccf64a71747fcbf9ae970aa7e9cd0c2c5feed3","tid":698505,"uid":154186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T18:17:23.000Z","msg":"甘你老母咩 你身份咪5p仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567ee5fe71960cf860d0c97b31c22ae64e7181fd","tid":698505,"uid":42601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T18:24:48.000Z","msg":"你係邊度長大?"},{"pid":"3b602c7f2ab776f2b5cd35a4a1e647472d06576a","tid":698505,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T18:30:30.000Z","msg":"來生不做中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3cbd840df43cc3f9d6f8d2bc6b519aff467685d","tid":698505,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T18:35:38.000Z","msg":"點解一個地方要有一個意思？地方只係偶然劃出嚟。"},{"pid":"23eb6efb3aef3f7f799747971c9e78c7f7a93684","tid":698505,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T